name: Bottomless by Lil Mahnaji and EM1T

metadata.name: On the Precipice of the Threshold
metadata.description:
What's down below?  
We’d rather forget so we can’t know.  
We're at the beginning,  
watching a vaporous flow. 
The past is an illusion,  
the future is confusion. 
The cyclical phase feels bottomless,  
requires immense will and faithfulness.  
Buidl, hod, and spedn,  
we'll all make it out in the edn.

Photo created during a foggy morning above the Bull of Wall Street by Lil Mahnaji and EM1T.
